// Go workspace file so editors (gopls) resolve the handbook's nested,
// buildable Go modules without opening each one as a separate workspace root.
//
// This repository is a multi-language engineering handbook; the root stays
// intentionally thin. Non-Go tooling ignores this file. As more buildable Go
// reference modules are added under golang/, list them in the `use` block.
go 1.26.0

use ./golang/reference/exampleservice
